messages.content:
Finding solitude in the hustle of cities, little did I know serenity thrives in unlikely pockets—between two buildings or even atop them. Captured in a frame, city skies are as peaceful as the hushed whispers between clouds. ++;
Cloud streets at twilight are my sanctuary, reminders of the gentle giants nature leaves when time and pace move otherwise. Until then, cities hold my solitude;
🌌🏙️ #CitySolitude #SkySanctuaries #PeaceInPerspective
